{"id":"api/core/HostListener","title":"HostListener","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/HostListener\", \"name\": \"HostListener\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1425-L1425\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1425-L1425\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"hostlistener\">HostListener<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#hostlistener\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個裝飾器，用於宣告要監聽的 DOM 事件，並提供在該事件發生時要執行的處理器方法。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decorator that declares a DOM event to listen for,\nand provides a handler method to run when that event occurs.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/HostListener#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>選項</th><th>說明</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#eventName\">\n          <code>eventName?</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">要監聽的事件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The DOM event to listen for.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#args\">\n          <code>args?</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">當該事件發生時傳給處理器方法的一組引數。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A set of arguments to pass to the handler method when the event occurs.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">當宿主元素髮出指定的事件時，Angular 會呼叫提供的處理程式方法，並使用結果更新繫結元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular invokes the supplied handler method when the host element emits the specified event,\nand updates the bound element with the result.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果處理程式方法返回 false，則在繫結元素上應用 <code>preventDefault</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If the handler method returns false, applies <code>preventDefault</code> on the bound element.</p>\n\n  <p>Further information is available in the <a href=\"api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\">Usage Notes...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"eventName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"eventname\">eventName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#eventname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1328-L1334\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1328-L1334\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">要監聽的事件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The DOM event to listen for.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            eventName?: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  <a id=\"args\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"args\">args<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#args\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1335-L1341\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1335-L1341\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">當該事件發生時傳給處理器方法的一組引數。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A set of arguments to pass to the handler method when the event occurs.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            args?: string[]\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子聲明瞭一個指令，它會為按鈕附加一個 <code>click</code> 監聽器，並統計點選次數。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example declares a directive\nthat attaches a click listener to a button and counts clicks.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'button[counting]'})\nclass CountClicks {\n  numberOfClicks = 0;\n\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('click', ['$event.target'])\n  onClick(btn) {\n    console.log('button', btn, 'number of clicks:', this.numberOfClicks++);\n  }\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: '&lt;button counting&gt;Increment&lt;/button&gt;',\n})\nclass App {}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下範例註冊了另一個 DOM 事件處理程式，它會偵聽全域 <code>window</code> 上的 <code>Enter</code> 按鍵事件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example registers another DOM event handler that listens for <code>Enter</code> key-press\nevents on the global <code>window</code>.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a> } from \"@angular/core\";\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: `&lt;h1&gt;Hello, you have pressed enter {{counter}} number of times!&lt;/h1&gt; Press enter key\nto increment the counter.\n  &lt;button (click)=\"resetCounter()\"&gt;Reset Counter&lt;/button&gt;`\n})\nclass AppComponent {\n  counter = 0;\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('window:keydown.enter', ['$event'])\n  handleKeyDown(event: KeyboardEvent) {\n    this.counter++;\n  }\n  resetCounter() {\n    this.counter = 0;\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可以在此處找到 <code>keydown</code> 和 <code>keyup</code> 事件的有效鍵名列表：https: <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values\">//www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The list of valid key names for <code>keydown</code> and <code>keyup</code> events\ncan be found here:\n<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values\">https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values</a></p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">請注意，鍵也可以組合，例如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('keydown.shift.a')</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Note that keys can also be combined, e.g. <code>@<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('keydown.shift.a')</code>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可用於事件名稱字首的全域目標名稱是 <code>document:</code> 、 <code>window:</code> 和 <code>body:</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The global target names that can be used to prefix an event name are\n<code>document:</code>, <code>window:</code> and <code>body:</code>.</p>\n\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - guide/attribute-directives\n - guide/change-detection-skipping-subtrees\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/migration-undecorated-classes\n - guide/styleguide\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/HostListener#args\n - api/core/HostListener#description\n - api/core/HostListener#eventName\n - api/core/HostListener#eventname\n - api/core/HostListener#hostlistener\n - api/core/HostListener#options\n - api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1328-L1334\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1335-L1341\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1425-L1425\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1328-L1334\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1335-L1341\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1425-L1425\n - https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values\n-->"}